revision.text: Possibly: Biblia sacra: integru[m] utriusq[ue] testamenti corpus co[m]plecte[n]s: diligenter recognita [&] eme[n]data. Cu[m] concorda[n]tis ac summariis simul et argume[n]tis: ad toti[us] intelligentia[m] biblie no[n] paru[m] co[n]duce[n]tib[us]. Insup[er] in calce eiusde[m]: annexe sunt nominu[m] Hebraicoru[m], Chaldeorum atq[ue] Grecorum accurate interpretationes. (Bible. Latin. 1526). (Parisiis [Paris]: Ex officina libraria vidue spectabilis viri Thielma[n]ni Kerver: sub signo unicornis invico sancti iacobi: ubi [&] venu[n]datur, M. D. xxvi. Octauo idus novembres [1526]). http://library.st-andrews.ac.uk/record=b2369576~S1
